{"tid":2250230,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港電台：澳洲參與美日印海上軍演　料觸怒中國","createTime":"2020-10-20T03:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T14:44:45.000Z","uid":290404,"like":188,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"272610ba897bee85ee834d3ad95bcbad5c82a03c","tid":2250230,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555679-20201020.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555679-20201020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=f2ce31c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555679-20201020.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=133d2595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555679-20201020.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲宣布參加今年11月與美國、日本和印度的「馬拉巴軍演2020」，<strong>輿論認為，此舉將會觸怒正在印太地區展開軍事擴張的中國。</strong><br />\n<br />\n澳洲聲明指出，海上軍演將令印度、美國、日本和澳洲這些「重要的區域防衛夥伴」連結，提升澳洲海軍戰力、加強緊密夥伴之間的共同行動能力，並且展示支持一個開放繁榮印太地區的共同決心，提升四國合作維護區域和平穩定的能力。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲上一次參加馬拉巴軍演，是在2007年。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本和澳洲傳媒認為，澳洲參加軍演將觸怒中國。</strong><br />\n<br />\n有印度前海軍軍官說，四國共同參與軍演，將有助反制中國在印太地區展開軍事擴張，又批評中國在印太地區興建軍港，操縱多個太平洋島國。"},{"pid":"15f1135ab074f6e390327f8ea6e3677ccc54df82","tid":2250230,"uid":134323,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"下，未嬲架？<br />\n礦石都唔買啦"},{"pid":"18f284c3972b7ea51374c700c6c22d39248fc12a","tid":2250230,"uid":187232,"like":119,"dislike":0,"score":119,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWZcWic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWZcWic.gif&h=28a1e90a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a447aa79b99de7b664cda56b2c103db6b07c3078","tid":2250230,"uid":371815,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-1